{"id":"mithcah","term":"Mithcah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Sweetness, one of the stations of the Israelites in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:28\">Num. 33:28</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:29\">29</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:28","Numbers 33:29"]}